: this is cardinality/dataflow preservation, not model-quality evaluation. REJECTION-GATE: rejected System because behavior text focuses on payload construction before posting.","test_description":"Run pipeline stages from finding collection through summary payload construction with varied finding sets (including edge metadata); assert summary count/content preserves all inline findings one-to-one.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.17,"Integration":0.78,"System":0.04,"Agentic":0.01,"Workflow":0}},{"behavior_id":6,"description":"Sequence with fixed findings (read diff, post inline, post summary) succeeds on a real PR.","minimum_level":"System","justification":"REAL-INFRA: explicitly requires real PR operations and live API calls. MOCK-HIDE: stubs miss auth, rate-limit, payload-shape, and endpoint-ordering failures. LLM-DEP: findings are precomputed/fixed, so model output quality is not under test. REJECTION-GATE: rejected Agentic because behavior text specifies fixed precomputed findings.","test_description":"Run automation end-to-end against a real repository PR using a fixed finding fixture; verify diff fetch succeeds, inline comments are created, and top-level summary posts with expected references.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.08,"System":0.88,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.01}},{"behavior_id":7,"description":"Full live run with model-generated findings completes correctly on a real PR without manual intervention.","minimum_level":"Agentic","justification":"LLM-DEP: success depends on real model-generated findings and their downstream handoff. REAL-INFRA: also uses real PR/API, but model dependence is the critical additional boundary beyond pure System. MULTI-STEP: sequence is end-to-end, but behavior text describes a single agentic analysis stage feeding deterministic posting, not multiple distinct agentic decision stages. REJECTION-GATE: rejected Workflow because no concrete behavior text requires multiple agentic stages in sequence.","test_description":"Execute full unattended pipeline on a real PR with live model analysis enabled; assert run completes, produces non-empty/valid findings, posts inline comments, and posts a consistent summary linked to created comments.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.02,"System":0.07,"Agentic":0.55,"Workflow":0.35}}]}
